subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Chris Nickson threw for a touchdown and ran for another and Vanderbilt beat a ranked opponent on its own field for the first time since 1992, upsetting No. 24 South Carolina, 24-17, in the Southeastern Conference opener for both teams.
